overview: The user initiated a request to significantly improve the aesthetic
  appeal of their sleep questionnaire application, which they felt was
  functional but lacked visual polish. The assistant took a structured approach,
  first conducting a comprehensive review of the app's existing visual
  components, global styles, and individual UI elements. Based on this analysis,
  the assistant identified several areas for improvement, including the generic
  color palette, plain backgrounds, and basic form styling. The key decision was
  to pivot to a calming, sleep-themed design. This involved updating the
  globals.css with a new color palette, revamping the QuestionnaireForm layout,
  enhancing the IntroSection with better visual hierarchy and feature cards, and
  refining the styling of CheckboxField, Checkbox, and Slider components. The
  outcome is a more professional and inviting user interface that aligns with
  the app's purpose.
